      "codeText": "from Crypto.PublicKey import RSA\nfrom Crypto.Util.number import inverse, long_to_bytes\n\np = ...\nq = ...\ne = 65537\nn = p * q\nd = inverse(e, (p-1)*(q-1))\nct = ...\npt = pow(ct, d, n)\nprint(long_to_bytes(pt))",
